@startuml
title UC-05. Отправить email-уведомление при сбое

participant "Result & SLA Module" as ResultSLA
participant "Notification Module" as Notification
database "Monitoring DB" as DB
participant "SMTP Server" as SMTP

ResultSLA -> Notification: sendFailureNotification(check_result_id, service_id, endpoint_id)

Notification -> DB: SELECT service, endpoint, check_result
DB --> Notification: failure details

Notification -> DB: SELECT responsibles by service_id
DB --> Notification: responsible list

loop for each responsible
    Notification -> Notification: build email subject and body
    Notification -> SMTP: send email(to=responsible.email)

    alt email sent
        SMTP --> Notification: success
        Notification -> DB: INSERT notification_log(status='SENT')
    else email sending failed
        SMTP --> Notification: error
        Notification -> DB: INSERT notification_log(status='FAILED')
    end
end

Notification --> ResultSLA: notification processing completed

@enduml